MORNING REPORT: PEOPLEWATCH 
Wild Wear: Sammy Hagar, the wild man lead singer of Van Halen, is introducing 
his own line of men's clothing that reflects the band's high-energy trademark. 
Red Rocker Hyper-Active Wear will be introduced at next week's Action Sports 
Retailer Convention in San Diego. Hagar said the full line of loose-fitting 
clothing will include more than 50 pieces. BETH KLEID 
